{"tid":1900023,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[689認証麵包鋪?] 品 穀 涉抄低醫護資料及老闆鬧人西客","createTime":"2020-02-27T03:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T01:04:57.000Z","uid":272518,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"185fcedd00571489105b77cf0009412fdb2ec6ee","tid":1900023,"uid":272518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"事緣早前呢間公司提供左8折優惠比醫護<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Crja55a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCrja55a.jpg&h=17cc0e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但竟然比人發現佢地竟然抄低人地個人資料 ( 唔知點解要抄, 出示証咪得囉 )<br />\n之後比人係 FB PAGE 嘈, 點解買你$2x 1個麵包 , <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平個幾蚊,要比人抄低資料呢?</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Adc4qYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdc4qYM.jpg&h=f5df5a46&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWf5UR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWf5UR6.jpg&h=3a344cdd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地解釋一時話驚自己員工濫用, 一時又話驚其他人濫用喎, 唔知邊句真邊句假<br />\n老闆Andrew 話 8折已經好多, 仲<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係IG 鬧 D人西客</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMWwQrD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMWwQrD.jpg&h=9a136249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間鋪頭之前仲比100毛宣傳過, 搞到之前排哂長龍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YZo3Gzd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYZo3Gzd.jpg&h=4932f4e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>現實其實係689 去既鋪頭</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dxqd3NG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDxqd3NG.jpg&h=047261a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇COMMENT D人都話你地D員工西口西面<br />\n緊係啦, 大部份都做唔長, 條條數計都盡<br />\nD面包都唔平下, 其實所有包裝野都係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">淘寶</span></strong>番黎....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4j2W9S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4j2W9S.jpg&h=7984b40e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n個OFFICE 真係好精彩 , 好多電線係空中 , 隔黎仲有好多雜物, 好危險呀!<br />\n<br />\n結論: 比少少著數你 記低你資料 好似某政黨囉, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">著數係我豪比你, 你屌我你就係西客!!</span></strong></span><br />\n傳送門 :<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1413822955587308/posts/2245976085705320/?d=n&amp;substory_index=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1413822955587308%2Fposts%2F2245976085705320%2F%3Fd%3Dn%26substory_index%3D0&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=886ba0fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1413822955587308/posts/2245976085705320/?d=n&amp;substory_index=0</a><br />\n利申: 前員工 ( one of the worst employee 上),"},{"pid":"4345747e81169441b444aec31db98f9df822d266","tid":1900023,"uid":272518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"b460832733bbce35627a993336a70f5f6d356c25","tid":1900023,"uid":272518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:42:13.000Z","msg":"診所護士都唔計醫護架wo<br />\n一定要係HA<br />\nwhy?"},{"pid":"c3d18c71cd89ed98ca6416b9ca57e41e6226ad36","tid":1900023,"uid":333077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"買個包都要抄低人地資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係藍店 不了"},{"pid":"8679ea75515fddf55b75ae0157b3d38ace2ab2dc","tid":1900023,"uid":272518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3d18c71cd89ed98ca6416b9ca57e41e6226ad36","tid":1900023,"uid":333077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"買個包都要抄低人地資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><